Producer application sends a number into kafka "test" topic.
<br/> in SparkCassandraConsumer, Spark consumes it and multiply by 2 and saves it into cassandra via SQL Streaming.
<br/> HadoopConsumer consumes the topic and writes it to a file named test in HDFS.
<br/> TODO: create a script to delete the resulting records in spark, cassandra, HDFS after test is done.